A prompt, in the context here, serves as a beginning or foundational statement or question to guide an AI program or user in generating additional text or responses. The mentioned example - writing a haiku about the importance of understanding AI - is one illustration of a prompt used with AI. After providing this prompt, the AI system generates responses, which can vary each time due to its probabilistic nature. These responses are guided by the initial prompt but can diverge in content and style, demonstrating the AI's ability to create varied and contextually relevant text.